#: 36263af822bf47fc9bdf08138a2197e6
msgid ""
"**Important:** Do not perform the steps described in this section until "
"**all** your Template and Standalone VMs have been upgraded as described "
"in the previous section. Also, do not shut down ``sys-net`` or ``sys-"
"firewall``, since you will not be able to start them again until after "
"the entire in-place upgrade procedure is complete."
msgstr ""

